tags: david tennant does a podcast with
summary:
David Tennant has a podcast now! 
According to his trailer, the starlit guests he’s interviewed so far include Whoopi Goldberg,...
body:
David Tennant has a podcast now!

According to his trailer, the starlit guests he’s interviewed so far include Whoopi Goldberg, Olivia Colman, Jon Hamm, Gordon Brown, Ian McKellen, Samantha Bee, Jodie Whittaker, Krysten Ritter, and Michael Sheen, though none of the episodes is out yet.

I like Tennant’s description for this “low concept” and “delicious” podcast: it’s just him and “some cool people, talking and stuff, on a podcast.” So far It sounds totally cool and chill. Can’t wait ‘til the first real episode.

Check it out. The name is “David Tannet Does a Podcast With …”
